## Switching to Gemini (Production)

The `GeminiClient` class is a thin abstraction designed for the Vertex AI swap. In `agent/gemini-client.js`, replace the Anthropic SDK block with:

```js
import { VertexAI } from '@google-cloud/vertexai';

const vertex = new VertexAI({ project: process.env.GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT, location: 'us-central1' });
const model  = vertex.getGenerativeModel({ model: 'gemini-2.0-flash-exp' });

// In analyzeFailure():
const result = await model.generateContent(prompt);
const raw    = result.response.candidates[0].content.parts[0].text;
```

The system prompt, JSON schema, and all tool integrations are identical regardless of LLM backend. See `cloud/agent-builder.yaml` for the full Google Cloud Agent Builder deployment config.

